# Input Data Pesawat

### Require
* Web Server
* PHP
* MYSQL

### Use
* Upload all file extension `.php` in directory root web
* Import mysql
* Edit conection in file `koneksi.php`
* Enjoy

### Demo
![Input Data Pesawat](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunDi3yansyah/input-ticket/master/screenshot/index.png)
